The '''midsummer festival''' was an annual celebration observed in [[Bright Tree Village/Legends|Bright Tree Village]] on the forest [[Moon/Legends|moon]] of [[Endor/Legends|Endor]]. In preparation for the festival, the [[Ewok/Legends|Ewoks]] made food and decorated the village with [[Color/Legends|colored]] chains of flowers. They then participated in numerous contests for activities such as basket-weaving, archery, and log-riding.

